Elixir lexer (source/turbo-core/lexers/LexElixir.cxx)
-----------------------------------------------------

Lexilla ships no Elixir lexer, so turbo carries its own. The lexer is an
original C++ state machine and contains no third-party code, but its token
inventory -- the keyword and guard lists, the set of lexical categories, and
the sigil semantics (lowercase sigils interpolate, uppercase ones do not) --
was transcribed as a specification from the Elixir TextMate grammar.

